Squizzy::

She ahd tried to get KitKat3 from leaving the lab, but couldn't stop 
the wolf bot.  She sighed and went back to making programs for 
Zardus.  She had completed one program that would make a bot a 
complete slave to Zardus is he wished it installed into a bot. 
She worked quietly in the lab, not kowing that there was another bot 
(LadyHawke) in the lab next door.
